    <b>Article 2 (Processing &amp; Retention Period of Personal Information) </b> <br />
    1	 The company processes and retains personal information under the period of retention and use of personal information stipulated by law or the period of retention and use of personal information agreed upon when collecting personal information from the data subject. <br />
    2	 The personal information processing and retention period of each law are as follows. We retain and use the relevant personal information for the above purposes from the date of agreement on collection and use. <br />
